const names = [
  {
    id: 1,
    name: 'Malina Syvoravong, Stylist and Recipe Developer',
    job: 'UI/UX, Webflow',
    image:
      'https://res.cloudinary.com/pearlmalt/image/upload/v1637009167/Screen_Shot_2021-11-15_at_12.45.51_PM_eckqg2.png',
    text:
      "Build and designed this website. We collaborated on her assets, and narrowed down to two photo sets she really loved.",
      linked: "https://msyvo.webflow.io/",
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    name: 'Emily Chao, Bay Area Experimental Filmmaker',
    job: 'HTML, CSS, JavaScript',
    image: 'https://res.cloudinary.com/pearlmalt/image/upload/v1637008869/Screen_Shot_2021-11-15_at_12.40.36_PM_dsssrc.png',
    text:
      'Hard coded this website from the ground up. Emily requested the grid of photos display in a random order on each click.',
      linked: 'https://github.com/pearlmalt/emilysSite',
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    name: 'Poetry Blog',
    job: 'HTML, CSS, JavaScript',
    image:
      'https://res.cloudinary.com/pearlmalt/image/upload/v1637027275/Untitled_design_5_ebiz3d.png',
    text:

    linked: 'https://github.com/pearlmalt/Node.js/tree/main/poetry',
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    name: 'Muse Map',
    job: 'HTML, CSS, Bootstrap',

      'https://res.cloudinary.com/pearlmalt/image/upload/v1637009366/Screen_Shot_2021-11-15_at_12.49.01_PM_ycas4i.png',
    text:
      'Built out a page for my phone app idea while using the Bootsrap library.',
    linked: 'https://github.com/pearlmalt/bootstrap/tree/main/Muse%20Map',
  },
  {
    id: 5,
    name: 'Jackie Katz, Political Theater Teacher',
    job: 'UI/UX, Webflow',
    image:
      'https://res.cloudinary.com/pearlmalt/image/upload/v1637009431/Screen_Shot_2021-11-15_at_12.50.16_PM_kjnqvp.png',
    text:
      'Jackie wanted a really enciting page articulating the many projects she has been involved in.',
    linked: 'https://katz.webflow.io/',
  },
  {
      id: 6,
      name: 'The Nautical History Preservation Society',
      job: 'UI/UX, Webflow',
      image:
        'https://res.cloudinary.com/pearlmalt/image/upload/v1637009487/Screen_Shot_2021-11-15_at_12.51.16_PM_u9w1ir.png',

        'Designed this non-profit website to educate on The NHPS mission.',
          linked: 'https://nhps.webflow.io/',
    },
    {
        id: 7,
        name: 'Newsletter-Signup',
        job: 'HTML, CSS, JavaScript, API, Node.JS',

          'Built a newsletter signup page with the Mailchimp API.',

      },
      {
          id: 8,
          name: 'Meeting Reminder',
          job: 'HTML, CSS React',
          image:
            'https://res.cloudinary.com/pearlmalt/image/upload/v1637026983/Untitled_design_4_zuj8go.png',
          text:
            'A neat meeting reminder made with React.JS.',

        },
        {
            id: 9,
            name: 'Drum Kit',
            job: 'Html, css, javascript, DOM',
            image:
              'https://res.cloudinary.com/pearlmalt/image/upload/v1637010055/Screen_Shot_2021-11-15_at_1.00.48_PM_yltsvq.png',

];
